合成。这些多方面的作用表明多胺代谢整合了氧化还原控制、翻译调节、表观遗传维持和自噬来决定细胞和有机体的寿命。虽然动物研究表明亚精胺和精胺具有明显的抗衰老作用，但人类临床证据仍然有限，可能由于生物利用度和代谢转化而产生不同的结果。未来的策略结合饮食或益生菌多胺增强、酶靶向抑制剂和个性化代谢干预措施有望延长健康寿命。总的来说，维持最佳的多胺稳态已成为对抗衰老和与年龄相关的疾病的关键方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/polyamine-metabolism-as-a-regulator-of-cellular-and-organismal-aging2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 11:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/polyamine-metabolism-as-a-regulator-of-cellular-and-organismal-aging</guid></item><item><title>科学家表示，视力丧失可以通过“重启”眼睛来逆转，而且只需 48 小时</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/scientists-say-vision-loss-may-be-reversible-by-rebooting-your-eye-and-it-takes-just-48-hours</link><description>如果您可以扳动重置开关并使您的视力恢复正常，会怎样？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-say-vision-loss-may-be-reversible-by-rebooting-your-eye-and-it-takes-just-48-hours2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 11:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/scientists-say-vision-loss-may-be-reversible-by-rebooting-your-eye-and-it-takes-just-48-hours</guid></item><item><title>SGLT2 抑制剂治疗非糖尿病性心力衰竭：为 PCP 提供成功装备</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/sglt2-inhibitors-for-nondiabetic-heart-failure-equipping-pcps-for-success</link><description>SGLT2 抑制剂曾经是糖尿病药物，现在是治疗心力衰竭的关键药物——即使对于没有糖尿病的患者也是如此。一份新的初级保健指南回顾了适应症、益处和实用处方技巧，以帮助临床医生将这些药物纳入常规心力衰竭护理中。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sglt2-inhibitors-for-nondiabetic-heart-failure-equipping-pcps-for-success.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 11:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/sglt2-inhibitors-for-nondiabetic-heart-failure-equipping-pcps-for-success</guid></item><item><title>表观遗传重塑和转座子介导的基因组不稳定性在衰老和长寿中的相互作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/the-interplay-of-epigenetic-remodelling-and-transposon-mediated-genomic-instability-in-ageing-and-longevity</link><description>抽象的。衰老和与年龄相关的疾病